.Dd 29 August 2008
.Os Python 2.x
.Dt CBANK 7 USD
.Sh NAME
.Nm cbank-new-charge
.Nd clusterbank command-line interface
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op options
.Ar project
.Ar amount
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Charge an
.Ar amount
of a resource to a
.Ar project .
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag
.It Fl u Ar user
Specify an associated
.Ar user .
.It Fl r Ar resource
Specify which
.Ar resource
to charge. (default specified in
.Pa /etc/clusterbank.conf )
.It Fl c Ar comment
Provide an informative
.Ar comment .
.It Fl n
Do not save the charge.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -item
.It
.Pa /etc/clusterbank.conf
Global configuration and defaults.
.El
